#. Tag: para
#: hardening.xml:4053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This randomizes the heap, stack, and load addresses of dynamically linked "
"libraries. Programs that run privileged or process network data are already "
"built using special compiler flags (PIE and _FORTIFY_SOURCE) to take even "
"more advantage of randomizing the text and data segments as well."
